Variable Declaration:-->

		Note:--> Variable declaration is usedefined
		
		Characters       		int abc=100;
		Characters+Numbers      int ab1=200;
		Characters_Underscore	int ab_c=400;
		
		Note:--> Same declaration we follow for class and method name.
		
		
		invalid declarations:-->
		
		With spaces        int ab cd=100;
		Startwithnumber	   int 10a=200;
		special characters int a-b=300;